es.uco.pw.data.common

Interface IDAO<T,E>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of object that the DAO manages.
    E - The type of identifier or key used to retrieve objects of type T.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ActivityDAO, AssistantDAO, CampamentDAO, CompleteInscriptionDAO, MonitorDAO, ParcialInscriptionDAO

    public interface IDAO<T,E>
    This interface represents a Data Access Object (DAO) common interface for managing objects of type T.
